name: Startup
tagline: A project that will promote the ideas of anyone around the world.
body:
### Welcome to Startup.
There are lot of awesome ideas around the world, like the one you have in mind. Our perspective is to promote your idea by giving paid and non-paid promotions
 
### How it help your idea
We provide us the maximum reach to your idea that brings you more user base to your customer base.

### Unique feature of us
* Fame to your concept.
* More user base
* Real world support (Financial and non-financial)


### Authors and Contributors
We are expecting contributors around the globe.
* Sooraj narayanan (@sooraj007) 

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? We are building our documentations.
